data.description: Location, location, location! Spacious brick ranch style home with open concept floor plan on a corner lot and conveniently located just minutes to Post!  Bright and open Kitchen with white cabinets, Stainless appliances, Granite counter tops, Formal Dining Room/Study, Great Room, Fireplace, 3 Bedrooms and 2 full Bathrooms and both Baths have ceramic tile. Inside Laundry, Large fenced backyard! Carport, Outside Storage. New HVAC and ductwork in May 2023, updated electrical in May 2023.  All Rooms are large.  New interior paint! Located in beautiful Cottonade subdivision close to shopping, schools, restaurants and just minutes to Ft Liberty.  This home is so close to Post, you can hit the snooze button and sleep in a little longer each morning!
